{"id":1105,"category_slug":"toeic","category_name":"TOEIC Listening","position":68,"title":"Conversation 38","subtitle":"Coffee Order Mix-Up","level":"B1","parts":19,"url":"https://dailydictation.com/exercises/toeic/conversation-38.1105/listen-and-type","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-38-2023-09-14-16-26-13/0-conversation-38.mp3","transcript":"Excuse me.\nThis isn't the drink I ordered.\nOh, really?\nWhat did you order again?\nWell, I ordered a large iced decaf latte,\nwith one shot of espresso,\nfour pumps of caramel syrup,\nsoy milk, and extra whipped cream on top.\nSo sorry about that.\nOh, I can't believe I mixed up your order.\nDo you mind waiting for a few minutes?\nI'll make you a new one.\nWell, mistakes happen.\nAnd, uh, don't worry about making a new one.\nI'll take it as it is since I'm in a bit of a rush.\nThat's very nice of you.\nPlease let me give you a 100% off drink coupon.\nYour next cup of coffee will be on the house.\nThanks. I appreciate it.","youtube_video_id":"","details_cached_at":"2026-06-15T21:00:07","challenges":[{"position":1,"content":"Excuse me.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-38-2023-09-14-16-26-13/1.mp3","time_start":0.25,"time_end":1.52},{"position":2,"content":"This isn't the drink I ordered.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-38-2023-09-14-16-26-13/2.mp3","time_start":1.52,"time_end":3.83},{"position":3,"content":"Oh, really?","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-38-2023-09-14-16-26-13/3.mp3","time_start":3.83,"time_end":5.63},{"position":4,"content":"What did you order again?","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-38-2023-09-14-16-26-13/4.mp3","time_start":5.63,"time_end":8.0},{"position":5,"content":"Well, I ordered a large iced decaf latte,","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-38-2023-09-14-16-26-13/5.mp3","time_start":8.23,"time_end":12.27},{"position":6,"content":"with one shot of espresso,","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-38-2023-09-14-16-26-13/6.mp3","time_start":12.27,"time_end":14.27},{"position":7,"content":"four pumps of caramel syrup,","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-38-2023-09-14-16-26-13/7.mp3","time_start":14.27,"time_end":16.41},{"position":8,"content":"soy milk, and extra whipped cream on top.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-38-2023-09-14-16-26-13/8.mp3","time_start":16.41,"time_end":19.69},{"position":9,"content":"So sorry about that.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-38-2023-09-14-16-26-13/9.mp3","time_start":20.46,"time_end":22.49},{"position":10,"content":"Oh, I can't believe I mixed up your order.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-38-2023-09-14-16-26-13/10.mp3","time_start":22.49,"time_end":25.37},{"position":11,"content":"Do you mind waiting for a few minutes?","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-38-2023-09-14-16-26-13/11.mp3","time_start":25.37,"time_end":28.03},{"position":12,"content":"I'll make you a new one.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-38-2023-09-14-16-26-13/12.mp3","time_start":28.03,"time_end":29.82},{"position":13,"content":"Well, mistakes happen.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-38-2023-09-14-16-26-13/13.mp3","time_start":30.32,"time_end":32.47},{"position":14,"content":"And, uh, don't worry about making a new one.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-38-2023-09-14-16-26-13/14.mp3","time_start":32.47,"time_end":36.06},{"position":15,"content":"I'll take it as it is since I'm in a bit of a rush.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-38-2023-09-14-16-26-13/15.mp3","time_start":36.06,"time_end":39.54},{"position":16,"content":"That's very nice of you.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-38-2023-09-14-16-26-13/16.mp3","time_start":40.0,"time_end":41.93},{"position":17,"content":"Please let me give you a 100% off drink coupon.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-38-2023-09-14-16-26-13/17.mp3","time_start":41.93,"time_end":46.3},{"position":18,"content":"Your next cup of coffee will be on the house.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-38-2023-09-14-16-26-13/18.mp3","time_start":46.3,"time_end":49.44},{"position":19,"content":"Thanks. I appreciate it.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-38-2023-09-14-16-26-13/19.mp3","time_start":49.98,"time_end":52.27}]}